{"type":"message","id":"a95633a8","parentId":"e5c8a494","timestamp":"2026-03-16T04:28:01.753Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-16 12:28:00 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_b3b3dc776df60982741679029db666e9 [msg:om_x100b544c2232e13cb3c2452897ae983]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b544c2232e13cb3c2452897ae983\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_b3b3dc776df60982741679029db666e9\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_b3b3dc776df60982741679029db666e9\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-03-16 12:28 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_b3b3dc776df60982741679029db666e9\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_b3b3dc776df60982741679029db666e9\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_b3b3dc776df60982741679029db666e9\"\n}\n```\n\n为你配置mcp:\n安装mcp, 配置参考如下， 顺带测试下功能是否正常： {\n \"mcpServers\": {\n    \"MiniMax\": {\n      \"command\": \"minimax-coding-plan-mcp\",\n      \"env\": {\n        \"MINIMAX_API_KEY\": \"sk-cp-8I-y0iNgSwdc8Pwe9mxmp0BtxzXHe0gUatEBBzCARdT8M4MGPQBCZhE5tGpmFrzBlhLGSr8A2B4UH2Wjk3lZ5vgammDMEWZaqikam6XPkmTYhhPgnhd0yHk\",\n        \"MINIMAX_API_HOST\": \"https://api.minimaxi.com\"\n      }\n    }\n  },\n  \"imports\": []\n}"}],"timestamp":1773635281750}}
{"type":"message","id":"434fca03","parentId":"a95633a8","timestamp":"2026-03-16T04:28:05.984Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想让我安装和配置 MiniMax MCP 服务器。我需要：\n\n1. 使用 mcporter 技能来安装 minimax-coding-plan-mcp\n2. 配置它\n3. 测试功能\n\n让我先读取 mcporter skill 看看怎么用。","thinkingSignature":"36545ee35ed296bc13f0639e59cf163bb57e9972f946867261b87e052042f0b5"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_sk6xdn199d83_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/admin/.openclaw/workspace/skills/mcporter/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5-highspeed","usage":{"input":20,"output":92,"cacheRead":16722,"cacheWrite":3337,"totalTokens":20171,"cost":{"input":0.000012,"output":0.0002208,"cacheRead":0.0010033199999999998,"cacheWrite":0.001251375,"total":0.002487495}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773635281751}}
{"type":"message","id":"c586a88e","parentId":"434fca03","timestamp":"2026-03-16T04:28:05.995Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_sk6xdn199d83_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: mcporter\ndescription: Use the mcporter CLI to list, configure, auth, and call MCP servers/tools directly (HTTP or stdio), including ad-hoc servers, config edits, and CLI/type generation.\nhomepage: http://mcporter.dev\nmetadata: {\"clawdbot\":{\"emoji\":\"📦\",\"requires\":{\"bins\":[\"mcporter\"]},\"install\":[{\"id\":\"node\",\"kind\":\"node\",\"package\":\"mcporter\",\"bins\":[\"mcporter\"],\"label\":\"Install mcporter (node)\"}]}}\n---\n\n# mcporter\n\nUse `mcporter` to work with MCP servers directly.\n\nQuick start\n- `mcporter list`\n- `mcporter list <server> --schema`\n- `mcporter call <server.tool> key=value`\n\nCall tools\n- Selector: `mcporter call linear.list_issues team=ENG limit:5`\n- Function syntax: `mcporter call \"linear.create_issue(title: \\\"Bug\\\")\"`\n- Full URL: `mcporter call https://api.example.com/mcp.fetch url:https://example.com`\n- Stdio: `mcporter call --stdio \"bun run ./server.ts\" scrape url=https://example.com`\n- JSON payload: `mcporter call <server.tool> --args '{\"limit\":5}'`\n\nAuth + config\n- OAuth: `mcporter auth <server | url> [--reset]`\n- Config: `mcporter config list|get|add|remove|import|login|logout`\n\nDaemon\n- `mcporter daemon start|status|stop|restart`\n\nCodegen\n- CLI: `mcporter generate-cli --server <name>` or `--command <url>`\n- Inspect: `mcporter inspect-cli <path> [--json]`\n- TS: `mcporter emit-ts <server> --mode client|types`\n\nNotes\n- Config default: `./config/mcporter.json` (override with `--config`).\n- Prefer `--output json` for machine-readable results.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773635285991}}
