{"type":"message","id":"fade4791","parentId":"e4eb9944","timestamp":"2026-03-16T04:49:05.721Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I realize that calling openclaw tool from within a script won't work as expected because this is a skill that should be used directly by the agent, not as a standalone script. Let me reconsider the approach.\n\nLooking at how the feishu skills work - they use the OpenClaw tool system directly. The skill definition should describe how to use the underlying tools.\n\nActually, the best approach is to:\n1. Update SKILL.md to describe the workflow clearly\n2. The skill will use existing tools: feishu_wiki_space, feishu_wiki_space_node, and feishu_mcp_create_doc\n\nLet me update the SKILL.md to be more comprehensive and explain the workflow.","thinkingSignature":"19dc7adfe3bef3747bba2881a8507a4ebd54c4797bd88277ef89c081c2574097"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_12dh1efkebwg_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"chmod +x ~/.openclaw/shared-skills/feishu-wiki-write/scripts/wiki_write.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5-highspeed","usage":{"input":39748,"output":189,"cacheRead":12787,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":52724,"cost":{"input":0.0238488,"output":0.00045359999999999997,"cacheRead":0.0007672199999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.025069619999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773636542270}}
