{"type":"message","id":"d2818827","parentId":"d23261e7","timestamp":"2026-03-16T04:49:44.957Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_b4ejrnytubvp_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"📦 feishu-wiki-write ✓ Ready\n\n写入飞书知识库文档。根据文件名和内容自动选择最合适的目录创建子文档并写入 Markdown 内容。\n使用方法：直接调用 skill，传入 filename 和 content 参数。\n\n\nDetails:\n  Source: openclaw-extra\n  Path: ~/.openclaw/shared-skills/feishu-wiki-write/SKILL.md\n\nTip: use `npx clawhub` to search, install, and sync skills."}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":2943,"aggregated":"📦 feishu-wiki-write ✓ Ready\n\n写入飞书知识库文档。根据文件名和内容自动选择最合适的目录创建子文档并写入 Markdown 内容。\n使用方法：直接调用 skill，传入 filename 和 content 参数。\n\n\nDetails:\n  Source: openclaw-extra\n  Path: ~/.openclaw/shared-skills/feishu-wiki-write/SKILL.md\n\nTip: use `npx clawhub` to search, install, and sync skills.","cwd":"/home/admin/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773636584948}}
{"type":"message","id":"89bb4fa8","parentId":"d2818827","timestamp":"2026-03-16T04:49:49.597Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The skill is registered and ready. Now I should summarize what I've created for the user.","thinkingSignature":"25c6451c057f572f95b83eea08e06526951abbe6390db2a9c325718621d7ee3a"},{"type":"text","text":"搞定啦！🦐\n\n---\n\n## ✅ 已创建 feishu-wiki-write Skill\n\n| 项目 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| **Skill 名称** | feishu-wiki-write |\n| **位置** | `~/.openclaw/shared-skills/feishu-wiki-write/` |\n| **状态** | ✅ 已注册 |\n\n---\n\n## 📋 Skill 功能\n\n根据文件名和内容自动：\n1. 获取知识库目录树\n2. 分析内容分类（技术文档、会议纪要、产品需求等）\n3. 在最合适的目录下创建子文档\n4. 写入 Markdown 内容\n5. 返回文档链接\n\n---\n\n## 🚀 使用方法\n\n直接告诉我，比如：\n\n> \"在知识库创建一份 API 设计文档，内容是...\"\n\n我就会帮你完成以下流程：\n- 分析内容 → 找到\"技术文档\"分类目录 → 创建文档 → 写入内容 → 返回链接\n\n---\n\n需要我现在就测试一下吗？比如创建一篇测试文档？🧐"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5-highspeed","usage":{"input":43535,"output":226,"cacheRead":12787,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":56548,"cost":{"input":0.026121,"output":0.0005424,"cacheRead":0.0007672199999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.027430619999999996}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773636584955}}
{"type":"message","id":"1d3c6e6a","parentId":"89bb4fa8","timestamp":"2026-03-16T04:50:44.755Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-16 12:50:43 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_b3b3dc776df60982741679029db666e9 [msg:om_x100b544c8ce110a4b299ee3d7d2b73c]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b544c8ce110a4b299ee3d7d2b73c\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_b3b3dc776df60982741679029db666e9\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_b3b3dc776df60982741679029db666e9\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-03-16 12:50 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_b3b3dc776df60982741679029db666e9\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_b3b3dc776df60982741679029db666e9\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_b3b3dc776df60982741679029db666e9\"\n}\n```\n\n请执行GitHub热榜调研任务：\n1. 访问 https://github.com/trending?since=daily 获取今日热榜\n2. 提取前10个热门项目\n3. 获取每个项目的详细信息（star数、描述、语言、README）\n4. 整理成调研报告：\n  - 项目名称和GitHub地址\n  - Star数和今日增长\n  - 项目描述\n  - 深度调研（功能、亮点、适用场景）\n  - 趋势洞察和开发者建议\n5. 完成后报告内容写入到飞书知识库，格式为Markdown，包含每个项目的GitHub链接。"}],"timestamp":1773636644749}}
