{"type":"message","id":"ebe96f9c","parentId":"c0dd3201","timestamp":"2026-03-16T04:52:49.659Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，看起来飞书已经配置好了。现在问题是工具调用方式。让我直接在当前会话中调用 feishu 工具来创建文档。但实际上，根据 OpenClaw 的架构设计，工具是在 agent 会话中通过工具注册机制提供的，而不是通过 CLI。让我尝试直接调用工具，但首先需要确认工具名称是否正确。根据之前的输出，工具名称应该是 `feishu_create_doc`。\n\n但是实际上，我无法直接在命令行中调用这些工具，因为它们是通过 Gateway WebSocket 注册到 agent 会话中的。\n\n让我尝试另一种方法：直接使用飞书开放平台 API 来创建文档。首先需要获取 tenant_access_token。","thinkingSignature":"2c73fcae59eb34ceae31db643a03e13f735f1bf1664d5c284fc28501cfe48f28"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_l4fwnz546y0t_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"APP_ID=\"cli_a93a5bdf09625cd2\"\nAPP_SECRET=\"jpTytLKpHDapaF0nt7gTpgOCi11kLeAr\"\ncurl -s -X POST \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/auth/v3/tenant_access_token/internal\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d \"{\\\"app_id\\\":\\\"$APP_ID\\\",\\\"app_secret\\\":\\\"$APP_SECRET\\\"}\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5-highspeed","usage":{"input":63688,"output":246,"cacheRead":12787,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":76721,"cost":{"input":0.0382128,"output":0.0005903999999999999,"cacheRead":0.0007672199999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.039570419999999995}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773636764807}}
