{"type":"message","id":"b646894e","parentId":"66b8129f","timestamp":"2026-03-16T04:56:46.098Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户让我把之前的文档写入知识库。让我先检查一下飞书 API 权限问题是否已经解决，然后尝试写入知识库。\n\n首先需要获取知识库信息，然后创建文档。","thinkingSignature":"c5359633c22636a4484a05df52815231e8940f85533be7e519ac9479dbb181b4"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_7dcruxio9apc_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"APP_ID=\"cli_a93a5bdf09625cd2\"\nAPP_SECRET=\"jpTytLKpHDapaF0nt7gTpgOCi11kLeAr\"\nTOKEN=$(curl -s -X POST \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/auth/v3/tenant_access_token/internal\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d \"{\\\"app_id\\\":\\\"$APP_ID\\\",\\\"app_secret\\\":\\\"$APP_SECRET\\\"}\" | grep -o '\"tenant_access_token\":\"[^\"]*\"' | cut -d'\"' -f4)\n\necho \"Token: $TOKEN\"\n\n# 获取知识库节点信息\ncurl -s \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/wiki/v2/spaces\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5-highspeed","usage":{"input":20,"output":229,"cacheRead":12787,"cacheWrite":65399,"totalTokens":78435,"cost":{"input":0.000012,"output":0.0005496,"cacheRead":0.0007672199999999999,"cacheWrite":0.024524625,"total":0.025853445000000003}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773636990431}}
