{"type":"message","id":"c54bb142","parentId":"2a2c4d80","timestamp":"2026-03-16T04:57:15.087Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"看起来有自动授权功能。但问题是应用本身没有开通权限。让我直接告诉用户需要手动去飞书开放平台添加权限。","thinkingSignature":"64f7c5e38f91c8d99a62adb41cf9eff3328fc66f6ddf6ef9d1ca35177505383b"},{"type":"text","text":"抱歉，权限问题还没解决 😅\n\n当前应用 `cli_a93a5bdf09625cd2` 缺少写入知识库需要的权限：\n\n```\n❌ 缺少权限：\n- wiki:wiki（知识库权限）\n- docx:document:create（文档创建权限）\n```\n\n## 🚀 解决方法\n\n1. 打开 **[飞书开放平台](https://open.feishu.cn/app/cli_a93a5bdf09625cd2/auth?q=wiki:wiki,wiki:wiki:readonly,wiki:space:retrieve,docx:document,docx:document:create&op_from=openapi&token_type=tenant)**\n\n2. 点击「开通权限」（需要管理员或应用管理员账号）\n\n3. 完成后告诉我，我再试一次！\n\n---\n\n或者，如果你不想用知识库，我也可以：\n- 📝 直接把报告内容发给你\n- 📧 发到你的飞书消息\n\n你选哪个？🦐"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5-highspeed","usage":{"input":67929,"output":228,"cacheRead":12787,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":80944,"cost":{"input":0.0407574,"output":0.0005472,"cacheRead":0.0007672199999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.042071819999999996}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773637030283}}
