{"type":"message","id":"9c27786f","parentId":"2bb3f517","timestamp":"2026-03-16T05:12:30.609Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"让我告诉用户需要添加什么权限。","thinkingSignature":"1f07626791bd8fab434ac9f8e77961d092518f92b8b4323e17ab33a60c9913c8"},{"type":"text","text":"已更新 feishu-wiki-write skill！🦐\n\n---\n\n## ✅ Skill 已更新\n\n| 项目 | 值 |\n|------|-----|\n| **知识库名称** | AI 知识库 |\n| **Space ID** | 7615846908665285857 |\n| **URL** | https://my.feishu.cn/wiki/settings/7615846908665285857 |\n\n---\n\n## ⚠️ 还需要权限\n\n当前应用还缺少以下权限，无法读写知识库：\n\n```\n❌ 缺少权限：\n- wiki:space:readonly（读取知识库）\n- wiki:node:create（创建文档）\n- wiki:node:update（更新文档）\n```\n\n请在 **[飞书开放平台](https://open.feishu.cn/app/cli_a93a5bdf09625cd2/auth?q=wiki:space:readonly,wiki:node:create,wiki:node:update,wiki:space:edit)** 添加这些权限：\n\n1. `wiki:space:readonly` - 读取知识库结构\n2. `wiki:node:create` - 创建知识库文档  \n3. `wiki:node:update` - 更新文档内容\n4. `wiki:space:edit` - 编辑知识库\n\n开通后告诉我，我再试一次！🚀"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5-highspeed","usage":{"input":80652,"output":277,"cacheRead":12787,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":93716,"cost":{"input":0.048391199999999995,"output":0.0006648,"cacheRead":0.0007672199999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.049823219999999994}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773637945651}}
