{"type":"message","id":"32d1fb3d","parentId":"50f1326d","timestamp":"2026-03-16T05:16:22.524Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"让我检查一下可能的问题。错误信息说需要 \"tenant needs read permission\"，这意味着应用本身（tenant）没有权限。可能需要：\n1. 添加权限\n2. 创建新版本\n3. 发布版本\n4. 可能还需要在知识库设置里添加应用\n\n让我给用户更明确的指引。","thinkingSignature":"79135b0468871b153fbbea806fcd30b8525e9ba455caa7ffa571a9df4d1fba96"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_vm6l3ckgt6ho_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"APP_ID=\"cli_a93a5bdf09625cd2\"\nAPP_SECRET=\"jpTytLKpHDapaF0nt7gTpgOCi11kLeAr\"\n\nTOKEN=$(curl -s -X POST \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/auth/v3/tenant_access_token/internal\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d \"{\\\"app_id\\\":\\\"$APP_ID\\\",\\\"app_secret\\\":\\\"$APP_SECRET\\\"}\" | python3 -c \"import sys,json; print(json.load(sys.stdin).get('tenant_access_token',''))\")\n\n# 尝试添加到知识库成员\ncurl -s \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/wiki/v2/spaces/7615846908665285857/members\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\n    \"member_type\": \"app\",\n    \"member_id\": \"'\"$APP_ID\"'\"\n  }'"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5-highspeed","usage":{"input":87577,"output":300,"cacheRead":12787,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":100664,"cost":{"input":0.052546199999999994,"output":0.0007199999999999999,"cacheRead":0.0007672199999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.05403341999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773638146323}}
