{"type":"message","id":"60c31104","parentId":"022b9e8e","timestamp":"2026-03-16T05:16:41.106Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"让我给用户更明确的指引。","thinkingSignature":"64a87bfe92166f3aedcf2129e3e34f75d1d6b36bd3152dc9337baf5bde866d1c"},{"type":"text","text":"抱歉，权限还没生效 😅\n\n---\n\n## ⚠️ 当前状态\n\n| 权限 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| 云文档 (docx) | ✅ 已开通 |\n| 知识库 (wiki) | ❌ 需添加并发布 |\n\n---\n\n## 🚀 请按以下步骤操作\n\n1. 打开 **[飞书开放平台](https://open.feishu.cn/app/cli_a93a5bdf09625cd2/auth)** \n\n2. 检查「**权限管理**」中是否已添加：\n   - `wiki:space:readonly`\n   - `wiki:space:edit` 或 `wiki:node:create`\n\n3. **如果已添加权限**：\n   - 进入「**版本管理与发布**」\n   - 创建新版本\n   - 发布上线\n\n4. **如果知识库需要单独授权**：\n   - 打开你的知识库：https://my.feishu.cn/wiki/settings/7615846908665285857\n   - 进入「**设置**」→「**权限管理**」\n   - 添加应用 `cli_a93a5bdf09625cd2`\n\n---\n\n搞定了告诉我，我再试一次！🦐"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5-highspeed","usage":{"input":88789,"output":256,"cacheRead":12787,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":101832,"cost":{"input":0.0532734,"output":0.0006144,"cacheRead":0.0007672199999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.05465502}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773638195577}}
