{"type":"message","id":"93e13a7e","parentId":"0493dd58","timestamp":"2026-03-16T10:11:45.438Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问北京有什么好玩的推荐。这是一个简单的问答，我可以根据我的知识给出建议，或者搜索一下北京最新的旅游信息。让我给用户一些北京好玩的推荐。","thinkingSignature":"6ad6e9fce296e9fd8de7aba55b69e8826fc861bc1ae92f98f552934d197aa13c"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_gbl79uc9yihz_1","name":"web_search","arguments":{"count":5,"date_after":"2025-01-01","query":"北京旅游攻略 2026 必玩景点推荐"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5-highspeed","usage":{"input":20,"output":95,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":118423,"totalTokens":118538,"cost":{"input":0.000012,"output":0.00022799999999999999,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.044408625,"total":0.044648625}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773655894737}}
{"type":"message","id":"971e0e54","parentId":"93e13a7e","timestamp":"2026-03-16T10:11:45.454Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_gbl79uc9yihz_1","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"error\": \"missing_brave_api_key\",\n  \"message\": \"web_search (brave) needs a Brave Search API key. Run `openclaw configure --section web` to store it, or set BRAVE_API_KEY in the Gateway environment.\",\n  \"docs\": \"https://docs.openclaw.ai/tools/web\"\n}"}],"details":{"error":"missing_brave_api_key","message":"web_search (brave) needs a Brave Search API key. Run `openclaw configure --section web` to store it, or set BRAVE_API_KEY in the Gateway environment.","docs":"https://docs.openclaw.ai/tools/web"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773655905441}}
{"type":"message","id":"bb05e762","parentId":"971e0e54","timestamp":"2026-03-16T10:11:53.192Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"没有搜索 API，但根据我的知识可以给出一些北京好玩的推荐。让我给用户一些建议。","thinkingSignature":"faaa7b2f8992fa3c2b48ebd32ce1181cb8f1f5a63e6ce54d97849f2f2ffceea3"},{"type":"text","text":"哇，要去北京啦！🎉 根据季节给你推荐一些好玩的：\n\n---\n\n## 🌸 春季（3-5月）北京必玩\n\n### 🏛️ 经典景点\n| 景点 | 亮点 |\n|------|------|\n| **故宫** | 春天的红墙绿瓦超美玉兰花开的季节 |\n| **颐和园** | 昆明湖划船看柳岸春晓 |\n| **天坛公园** | 春花烂漫，大爷大妈晨练超热闹 |\n| **长城（八达岭/慕田峪）** | 春季登高望远 |\n\n### 🌸 赏花圣地\n- **北海公园** - 白塔配桃花\n- **中山公园** - 郁金香展\n- **元大都遗址公园** - 海棠花溪\n- **玉渊潭公园** - 樱花节\n\n### 🛤️ 新晋打卡地\n- **北京环球影城** - 哈利波特园区超火\n- **首钢园** - 工业风拍照圣地\n- **隆福寺** - 潮流文创区\n\n### 🍜 必吃美食\n- 铜锅涮肉、东来顺\n- 炸酱面（海碗居、方砖厂69号）\n- 豆汁儿+焦圈（挑战一下！）\n\n---\n\n## 💡 小贴士\n\n- 🌬️ 3月北京还有沙尘暴可能，记得戴口罩\n- 🚇 地铁很方便，建议办一卡通\n- 🎫 故宫提前7天预约！\n\n你是出差还是旅游呀？待几天？我可以给你更具体的路线～ 🦐"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5-highspeed","usage":{"input":105826,"output":372,"cacheRead":12795,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":118993,"cost":{"input":0.0634956,"output":0.0008927999999999999,"cacheRead":0.0007677,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0651561}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773655905450}}
